Package com.sri.ai.grinder.polynomial.core

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultMonomial
    Default implementation of the Monomial interface.
    DefaultPolynomial
    Default implementation of the Polynomial interface.
    MonomialSignatureComparator
    A monomial M1 comes before another monomial M2 if it has higher degree or if their degree are the same wrt to a tuple of factors F iff signature(M1, F) is lexicographically larger than signature(M2, F).
    PolynomialIntegration
    Utility class for performing indefinite and definite integration on polynomials.
    PolynomialSummation
    Utility class for computing the summation of a given polynomial.
